{"type": "article", "id": 22318, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-02-16T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 12798, "name": "Masquespacio"}, {"id": 8334, "name": "yuue"}, {"id": 23436, "name": "THINK Packaging"}, {"id": 23437, "name": "Eleftheria Stamati"}, {"id": 23438, "name": "Atelier-D"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115133o5ah3TLWnNQgmDIy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>toadstool by masquespacio &amp; missana</h2>\n<p>这套家具名为 toadstool（毒菌），包括沙发、座位和边桌。桌面和座位面是绿色、蓝色、红色和粉色的软垫，搭配在一起有种孟菲斯的风格，造型可爱而颜色鲜艳。彩色绒垫下的支撑使用了木材、金属或大理石，有了不同材料的冲击，增加了趣味性。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152752TsDWnxrA0bqOEMQJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5403423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152752vXNYsrkbLlqVS4Bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79462103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152753C9D3GukmlJ8nKcOj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152753SOmvs2YpBzeG5jbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>One Piece by yuue</h2>\n<p>这是一套实木做的桌面收纳小件，每一块有 35 厘米长，上面刻出了不同形状的凹槽，一侧是相连的圆孔，另一侧是长方条的凹槽，可以将手机、各类笔插在其中。不同的收纳小件的凹槽有些微的不同，明亮的颜色和文具本身成为桌面的装饰。设计团队 yuue 是创立于德国的中国设计团队，<a href=\"http://www.yuue-design.com/works_zh/one-piece_zh/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152754PuTkGgwBlzYQeKZW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152754W23aVCP6oyR8NevX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152755U4Bz6Ihk2ELjHi7r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152755Dw08jPxJQHbghCvq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>The Mechanics of Black by Eleftheria Stamati</h2>\n<p>希腊的艺术家 Eleftheria Stamati 设计了一根双面穿戴的项链，其实是披在肩上的。吊坠利用几何原理和透视关系设计出带有立体感的图案，像是一个长方体或多个长方体，并特意空出了一根支柱，搭配着很细的链子，有种空灵感。正反两个吊坠恰好朝着两个不同的方向，突出了它的立方体视觉感受。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152755zoItj4lGuwNkcY0S.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152756HJQRVOst7DGv6i1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152756B3DPhurYkEO59pfb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152757AjK8gsobkXLq4Hpc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152757eSZp5QKlBsjvt8Ib.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>checkers set by Atelier-D </h2>\n<p>这是一套很有手工感的象棋，是胡桃木做的。每一颗象棋像小的纽扣，用深浅两色来区分。棋盘上使用激光蚀刻的技术，在需要加深的区域刻上密集的弧形波纹，使棋盘既有原本的木纹，也能做成深浅相间的网格。加拿大设计师 AtelierDmontreal 手工做出这套象棋，售价 150 加元，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/ca/listing/263939763/wooden-checkers?ref=shop_home_feat_2\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152757oAsGxCY8ufdLXjwl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152758MNfoRYLx65FaUeVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152758pJDOrPQCghtYUoZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152759EpctIbBfTNKChGAY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152759W3MknIXEN6ed4rvi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>ArcBicycle by TU Delft 学生团队</h2>\n<p>这是荷兰代尔夫特理工大学的学生设计团队设计的 3D 打印自行车，由 MX3D 公司协助完成。他们结合弧焊技术开发一款 3D打印机，通过电弧产生的高温熔化金属，然后制作成金属结构。车的框架结构是分别打印的，经过人工焊接，它的重量与钢架自行车一致，是探索 3D 打印中型物品的尝试。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152800iLSQsjZrgn2Db5qI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152801Q5hTmaIcGdjq3xpW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071528013bavRkTFPqmI19Ms.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152802hAY98CXJvVFSo10O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152802PFCBWbNtV1AOiwDx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>BLACK ARROW CANDLES by THINK Packaging</h2>\n<p>这是澳大利亚的一家专做蜡烛的品牌  Black Arrow Candles 的蜡烛包装，外形像一个被切过的木桩，上下有年轮一样的线条，四周有潮湿纹路的痕迹。他们宣称蜡烛是从大豆中提取原料，很天然，包装上也呼应了天然的特征。设计方 THINK Packaging 从罗宾汉射中木桩的原型中找到灵感，要从中一剖为二打开，带玻璃杯的蜡烛就镶嵌在了中心，有珍贵之意。<a href=\"http://blackarrowcandles.com.au\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152803FUIhPTJ4t7MA5Sao.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152803r8BoFiKU5lZ2WzMm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152803n2UjlVZbBTO1fAKm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071528047dmCIM8bEWTtoScQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607152804jLvRabO0ZU769cDg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}